data.description: Welcome home to this 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home on 5.1 acres in the beautiful Gore, VA. Walk into the front door to the open floor plan upstairs. Living room and kitchen run seamlessly together to create a great entertainment space. 2 bedrooms and 1 full bath finish the upstairs. In the fully finished basement, you will find the laundry area, bedroom, full bath and an additional room which can be used as the 4th bedroom. Outside, there is a large 23x30 garage with an unfinished apartment above. This home offers privacy in a very well kept subdivision. Live in the main house, and let your imagination run wild in the almost 700 square foot area above the garage. The owners have taken pride in this home, and have made this home adorable. Stay tuned and book your showing today!
